        "description": "Unlock the power of spatial understanding with Reality Ruler: 3D Measurement in MR! Our app utilizes the device's pass-through mode to turn your environment into a digital workspace for measurement.\n\nFeatures:\n\nMeasure Line Lengths: Draw lines in real space and get their lengths instantly.\nArea Calculations: Evaluate the area of polygons, rectangles, and circles with simple gestures.\nAngles: Get precise angles between intersecting lines in 3D space.\nVolumetrics: Estimate the volume of 3D shapes like cuboids, cylinders, cones, and spheres.\nReality Ruler offers an intuitive interface and simple controls, making it easy for anyone to get started. Whether you're a student learning geometry, a carpenter planning a project, or simply someone who wants to better understand the space around them, Reality Ruler provides an accurate and interactive way to measure the world.\n\nTurn your Headset into a powerful measurement tool with Reality Ruler: 3D Measurement in MR.",
